, "replies": 3, "created": 1781462491000, "id": "2066229563286311056", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1667984522732773376/e8R6vMh9_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Bill Mitchell", "username": "mitchellvii"}, "content": "The Democrat Party is headed for abject humiliation on November 3rd.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 16}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASss0nfQC", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 60, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8679784, "raw_content": "", "author": "Sea_Still", "created": 1781452039544, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "SBOJ_JOBS", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.americanthinker.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASss0nfQC.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.americanthinker.com/blog/2026/06/a_trump_executive_order_threatens_mail_in_ballot_fraud.html", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "A Trump executive order threatens mail-in ballot fraud.\n\nAmerica\u2019s fate hangs in the balance of a postal scale. ", "last_comment_created": 1781457711799, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 60, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "America\u2019s fate hangs in the balance of a postal scale.", "large_image": "1ZqEvnG6KuL3BUQi.png", "title": "A Trump executive order threatens mail-in ballot fraud"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASss0oD3N", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 44, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8679915, "raw_content": "This is just the start of a thought. There\u2019s no supporting evidence gathered at this point.\n\nWhen looking at the countries where all the immigrants flooding into Europe and the United States originate from, many have seen massive population spikes in the past century, and especially the past 50 years. Where did poor, dirty, uneducated countries gain the momentum to see such growth?\n\nIs it possible Christian charity organizations and government-funded NGOs, operating out of pure empathy for those less fortunate than people in Western countries, did this? How? Through programs which provided clean drinking water, ample food, and basic healthcare, such as vaccines, to societies which did nothing to earn those benefits.\n\nGifting those innovations, which greatly extend life expectancy, while not considering the second and third order effects of helping the people immediately at hand when implemented, led to population explosions. The end results of solutions to the very problems people throughout history have needed to solve by technological advancement, commerce, the development of social structures in order to thrive were suddenly just there. They didn\u2019t have to earn them, nor understand the likely effects on their nations.\n\nStruggling economies built on what the locals had been able to construct for themselves were far from ideal, but still sustained their populations within reason. Once the natural barriers to unchecked population growth were artificially removed, the birth rates swelled, and the local economies collapsed under the added weight. That left billions of people who wouldn\u2019t normally have been born in situations where they have absolutely no opportunities in their home countries.\n\nDid the Western world unintentionally feed the mechanism by which its existence may be undone? Has Christian generosity helped create the most dangerous threat Christianity may ever face?\n\nThis may be the largest case of \u201cno good deed goes unpunished\u201d in human history.", "author": "GuidedDisinfo", "created": 1781458059823, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Wrexxis780", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Na\u00efve Christian Charity And Liberal NGOs - Major Contributing Factors To The Decline Of Western Civilization?", "last_comment_created": 1781465664392, "content": "<p>This is just the start of a thought. There\u2019s no supporting evidence gathered at this point.</p>\n<p>When looking at the countries where all the immigrants flooding into Europe and the United States originate from, many have seen massive population spikes in the past century, and especially the past 50 years. Where did poor, dirty, uneducated countries gain the momentum to see such growth?</p>\n<p>Is it possible Christian charity organizations and government-funded NGOs, operating out of pure empathy for those less fortunate than people in Western countries, did this? How? Through programs which provided clean drinking water, ample food, and basic healthcare, such as vaccines, to societies which did nothing to earn those benefits.</p>\n<p>Gifting those innovations, which greatly extend life expectancy, while not considering the second and third order effects of helping the people immediately at hand when implemented, led to population explosions. The end results of solutions to the very problems people throughout history have needed to solve by technological advancement, commerce, the development of social structures in order to thrive were suddenly just there. They didn\u2019t have to earn them, nor understand the likely effects on their nations.</p>\n<p>Struggling economies built on what the locals had been able to construct for themselves were far from ideal, but still sustained their populations within reason. Once the natural barriers to unchecked population growth were artificially removed, the birth rates swelled, and the local economies collapsed under the added weight. That left billions of people who wouldn\u2019t normally have been born in situations where they have absolutely no opportunities in their home countries.</p>\n<p>Did the Western world unintentionally feed the mechanism by which its existence may be undone? Has Christian generosity helped create the most dangerous threat Christianity may ever face?</p>\n<p>This may be the largest case of \u201cno good deed goes unpunished\u201d in human history.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 44, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsrzfofI", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 917, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8678930, "raw_content": "", "author": "CyanScales", "created": 1781398446925, "profile_picture": "1cOg4Zdci1jH", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DrVSGGEOTUSPhD", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsrzfofI.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/adm3KgQljNMt.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/6UH94HzjQe0Yy